title: Wrestling 411 - Episode 22: Augsburg head coach Mark Matzek from January 14, 2009

description: Episode 22 of Wrestling 411 featured Augsburg head wrestling coach Mark Matzek as he talked about his Auggies' championship at the NWCA National Duals in Division III.
